12 entity from which the tax credits have been allocated and shall not
13 be limited to One Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00) for single
14 individuals or limited to Two Thousand Dollars ($2,000.00) for
15 married persons filing a joint return.
16 4. On or before April 30, 2024, and once every two (2) years
17 thereafter, such scholarship-granting organization and educational
18 improvement grant organization shall electronically submit to the
19 Oklahoma Tax Commission, the Governor, President Pro Tempore of the
